  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the steamer and prepare a large leaf for steaming.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the rice flour, coconut palm sugar, and baking powder.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the unsweetened almond milk, rapeseed oil, large egg, vanilla extract, and almond extract.",
    "Add the wet ingredients to the dry ingredients and mix until well combined.",
    "Add the strawberries and blueberries to the mixture and fold in gently.",
    "Place the mixture onto the prepared leaf, leaving a 1 inch border around the edges.",
    "Fold the leaf over the filling and steam for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and let cool for 5 minutes.",
    "Drizzle with honey before serving."
  ],
